description:
# RDM.dev - GUI for Redis

	
RDM (aka Redis Desktop Manager)— is a cross-platform open source Redis DB management tool (i.e. Admin GUI).

The installed application can be found at: 
%PROGRAMFILES(X86)%\RDM\rdm.exe
summary: A Redis DB management tool (i.e. Admin GUI) to replace a hundreds of slow and ugly tools for redis.
author: Igor Malinovskiy
